{"tid":1333180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（721買物資！）灣仔區有賣物資嘅店舖清單，歡迎有心人士出錢出力","createTime":"2019-07-19T14:58:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T16:40:51.000Z","uid":82829,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d1dea2454c39454d95a45a08ec2b295dbb0bad10","tid":1333180,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:58:38.000Z","msg":"（前言）大家好，我第一次開連登a/c，第二次寫文。我自己平時係個好普通嘅90後學生，遊行、集會都係自六月起先開始接觸同參與，但承擔風險嘅能力有限，所以都無試過衝到最前。我相信好多人嘅情況都同我差唔多，想為香港做多幾步，但又唔知可以邊度入手。所以我打算趁黎緊遊行仲有兩日，盡快寫呢篇文俾你哋參考吓。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就係每個人都幫手出少少錢，出少少力，買啲其他人會需要用嘅物資。</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uSRTTi3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuSRTTi3.png&h=a1f51537&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rdti4re.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRdti4re.png&h=0b9f76c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">個List咩黎？</span></ins></strong><br />\n呢個Excel係我同幾個朋友一齊整嘅，紀錄嘅係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">721遊行路線一帶</span></strong><span style=\"color: red;\">可以買到有用物資嘅舖頭</span>（駱克道、SOGO、皇后大道東為界）。當中包括常用嘅頭盔、3M眼罩、N95口罩、索帶、長遮、浮板、etc.<br />\n<br />\nDrive版本<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1x6zXeAE_vwbkJbDP9K79dhpgDBJKt-xX/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1x6zXeAE_vwbkJbDP9K79dhpgDBJKt-xX%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=6pEOCw3Iqoz%2FZ73NBW83JwZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=00d3ceb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1x6zXeAE_vwbkJbDP9K79dhpgDBJKt-xX/view?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n下載版<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vR652KqyLCum3fApHfQmLuLmiFp2Ub5_PzpZYP7j5pBTy2L68Chf8FbMAcRBA2dxQ/pub?output=xlsx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2Fe%2F2PACX-1vR652KqyLCum3fApHfQmLuLmiFp2Ub5_PzpZYP7j5pBTy2L68Chf8FbMAcRBA2dxQ%2Fpub%3Foutput%3Dxlsx&d=6pEOCw3Iqoz%2FZ73NBW83JwZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=ba3838ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vR652KqyLCum3fApHfQmLuLmiFp2Ub5_PzpZYP7j5pBTy2L68Chf8FbMAcRBA2dxQ/pub?output=xlsx</a><br />\n<br />\n喺黎緊兩日或者遊行當日，你可以視乎需要，去呢啲地方進行補給。如果你有閒錢同人力，我希望各位善長仁翁可以買多少少，分享俾其他有需要嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">咁樣做有咩野用？</span></ins></strong><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">保護好自己</span>。依家警犬愈黎愈猖狂，就算你係和理非都照樣摳。無人知721警犬會退化到咩程度，我個人建議參與黎緊遊行嘅人最起碼買定防護用具，<span style=\"color: red;\">簡單d講準備full gear</span>，保護好自己好緊要。<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">就算自己用唔著，都可以分俾人幫吓人</span>。喺現場嘅都知你<span style=\"color: red;\">每帶多個頭盔，現場就會少一個人喺無防護嘅情況下比警犬扑穿頭</span>。當然現實就無咁理想，但聊勝於無，頭盔一個先幾十蚊左右，有機會救人一命嘅野，小弟都會懇求大家多啲去買。<br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: red;\">一齊分散金錢同人力嘅負擔</span>。一個頭盔幾十蚊，百個就係幾皮野。就算夠錢買，夠唔夠力一個人搬都係問題。大家都知現場能調度嘅物資始終有限，如果每個遊行人士可以幫手買啲有用嘅物資，其實係能大幅分散呢啲負擔。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Excel File使用須知：</span></ins></strong><br />\n1. 請認清需要先買，避免浪費。有時有啲朋友行得前啲，<span style=\"color: red;\">你可以問吓佢哋要啲咩物資，確認完後Filter番相應物資再決定去邊度買</span>。如果問唔到，會建議優先買頭盔、眼罩、長遮、口罩（非普通口罩）、水同乾糧。<br />\n<br />\n2. 請注意如果買物資支援煲底，有機會俾警犬charge你協助非法集會。（如有錯請指正）所以記住呢個風險，呢啲事發夢先好做。<br />\n<br />\n3. 記住喺香港行街買野，警犬都係可以話你形跡可疑，所以買物資嘅時候自己小心。<br />\n<br />\n4. <span style=\"color: red;\">留意大部分有賣常用物資嘅舖頭係唔做禮拜日</span>orzz，建議可以早兩日買定/搵朋友買定/喺自己嗰區自己買。遊行當日請Filter走星期日休息日嘅舖頭。<br />\n<br />\n5. 物資價錢以查詢當日（最近）為準，但唔排除會臨時加價。請預鬆少少Budget。<br />\n<br />\n6. 離開集會或你確定自己用唔著買番黎嘅物資時，希望你可以將你嘅物資留俾其他有需要嘅人。但切記要好好思考自己係咪真係唔使再用，保護自己都好緊要。<br />\n<br />\n7. 如果你當日有用Google map搵舖頭，<span style=\"color: red;\">記得嗰晚Del曬d紀錄佢</span>。<br />\n<br />\n8. 一個人嘅力量同金錢（至少我係）有限，量力而為，適當時可以搵人幫手（警犬唔係人）<br />\n<br />\n後記<br />\n考慮到遍地開花嘅情況，如果今次條List有用幫到手，我同我朋友會搵時間做埋其他區嘅清單，但呢啲野都可以遍地開花架啫，我都會鼓勵各區嘅熱心人士可以為大家提供有用嘅資訊。<br />\n<br />\n總之，721香港人加油，唔好出事。<br />\n<br />\n（因為上一篇應該太悶所以無人睇，今次試吓Display得好d）"},{"pid":"2787b08f3f31da7b5be354b01fd23eb7d9e01fb6","tid":1333180,"uid":82829,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:59:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原po<br />\n（721買物資！）灣仔區有賣物資嘅店舖清單，歡迎有心人士出錢出力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1330460\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1330460</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"50cb2677c3502244e984185da9269e05089fa553","tid":1333180,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T15:03:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>【Hongkongers! Assemble! 】</strong></span><br />\n光復香港！沒有暴民，只有暴政！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kVURRBwauKE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkVURRBwauKE&d=6pEOCw3Iqoz%2FZ73NBW83JwZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=b7d143d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kVURRBwauKE</a><br />\n<br />\n不割蓆 不篤灰 不分化 不捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n 一、正式撤回修例<br />\n 二、取消暴動定性<br />\n 三、撤銷所有抗爭者控罪<br />\n 四、成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 五、立即實行真正雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F8Nr2YF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF8Nr2YF.jpg&h=93a6d743&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721! HONGKONGERS! ASSEMBLE!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>[721] 成日話宣傳不足，如果話夾錢落Youtube廣告Ad有無人支持？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1332224/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1332224/page/1</a></strong>"},{"pid":"f0c3a367f7d584022447817174b89898b59ce41f","tid":1333180,"uid":280877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:16:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"187a5252277e473ec62a26b3315425e719e03c1d","tid":1333180,"uid":81680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:19:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fc61ca2dc982d968b794a2d07e22ea54a22dc7c","tid":1333180,"uid":12146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:21:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />此風不可長"},{"pid":"32e635105f95ecbb68e21d264e7348894fd120b8","tid":1333180,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:22:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc3e5f7955889c819d0bee9e2e4cb062a2754eec","tid":1333180,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:22:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">今舖721大家真係要醒醒定定，認認真真，手足們要齊上齊落</span></span>"},{"pid":"cede05aa1d0a69375c280461d55351e9000295ab","tid":1333180,"uid":47875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:31:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916ce1078b46d3f58f0cbd1a83323949296d1e42","tid":1333180,"uid":258055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:33:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d537b3a68159540056ba7572bd63ee9639186ee2","tid":1333180,"uid":143708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:36:33.000Z","msg":"push 721見"},{"pid":"6df442c8c7770294893b2aae69654e48ae0a356d","tid":1333180,"uid":202224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:38:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d167d86ac00611bdd4d1cfcb783f2089ae35184e","tid":1333180,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:38:35.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"73be5db1b69c3e0a6145e619e08493f42a23a60f","tid":1333180,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:40:51.000Z","msg":"721見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}